_:N16f0461a3e9e41c1bc13d7b0b06d0c7f <http://schema.org/text> "UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) is responsible for making millions of decisions every year about who has the right to visit or stay in the country, with a firm emphasis on national security and a culture of customer satisfaction for people who come here legally. " .
